title: Eli Lilly hits $1 trillion market value, a first for a health-care company
summary: The pharmaceutical giant Eli Lilly's stock has been riding the skyrocketing demand for its weight loss injection Zepbound and diabetes treatment Mounjaro.

title: House Democratic leader gets in fiery clash as he defends ACA tax credit extension plan
summary: The fight over the ACA tax credits was at the center of the 43-day shutdown, which ended last week without a clear solution on health care.
